name: Professional Logo Design
description:
So you want a logo design?
We have a special startup price right now.
We have already created tons of unique, creative, custom and killer designs, which were all express delivered to their customers. We can create a new one or modify an already existing logo.
What's included:
1 High quality logo with UNLIMITED REVISIONS and MONEY BACK GUARANTEE in any failure.
If you need special things, take a look at the extras.
The vector file is UNLIMITED resizable without ANY image quality loss.

Logo will take 7 days in average, but 1 day express delivery is also available.
